      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Grid Convergence Index (GCI) must be below 2% for the hemolysis index QoI on the finest mesh used in the regulatory submission.",
      "rationale": "Richardson-extrapolation-based GCI computed on three meshes yields GCI of 4.7% for the hemolysis index at the highest-shear operating point. This exceeds the 2% threshold, placing achieved level at 3 rather than the required 4."
    },
    {
