      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Predicted hemolysis index must lie within experimental uncertainty bands for at least 4 of 5 operating points; comparison metric must include both bias and precision error.",
      "rationale": "Predictions fall within experimental uncertainty at 3 of 5 operating points. Bias and precision metrics are reported but the 4-of-5 threshold is not met, yielding achieved level 3 versus required level 4."
